title: HSE Extreme Sports Club Recommends Spending Vacations in Mountains (Higher School of Economics)
text: ( Source : Higher School of Economics ) HSE Extreme Sports Club is inviting students, lecturers, alumni and their friends to spend their New Year holiday (January 2-9) at Gudauri , one of the best ski resorts in Georgia . Registration is open
